timeline.bodyText:
Since geocodingManager.getOfflineAreaName(bounds) is an async operation, should it be modeled as a Single<>? If not, the UI might block while waiting for addAreaAndEnqueue() to finish. It might look something like:
return geocodingManager.getOfflineAreaName(bounds)
    .map(areaName => OfflineArea.newBuilder()....setName(areaName).build())   
    .flatMapCompletable(this::enqueueTileDownloads);
